The Department of Transportation saidthat an administrative law judge had recommended that smallpackage service between the United States and Tokyo be grantedto Federal Express Corp &lt;FDX>.    A final decision by the department is expected within 90days.    In addition, the department said the law judge recommendedthat backup service be granted to &lt;Orion Air Inc>. The order,if finally approved, would be for five years in the case ofFederal and one year in the case of Orion. Reuter&#3;